Former Liverpool legend Gary McAllister has been attacked in Leeds city centre on Saturday night.<br />
<br />
According to former teammate Dominic Matteo, &ldquo;Gary was hospitalised, he lost three teeth in the attack and had plastic surgery on his lip needing 12 stitches. &ldquo;The attacker is thought to be American, and due to the severity of the injuries may have been wearing a &lsquo;knuckle duster&rsquo; or similar.&rdquo;
